                    <h3 class="header3">Residence History</h3>
                    <p class="history__text header4">Two regions merge into one world in the landscape that you can enjoy from here and the two apartments, called Raffaello and Leonardo, the memento of an ancient language used by local farmers, have been restored with the utmost respect of materials and local traditions. 
                    The excellent geographical location of Ridolfi Residence allows our guests to easily visit historical and beautiful places.</p>
