                        </div>
                        <div class="history__place__title header3">
                            Ridolfi
                        </div>
                        <p class="history__place__text header6">
                        The Residence, a possession of the Church until 1860, acquired by the Ridolfi family, became a farmhouse and today it is a place of rest and serenity for those who want to relax their mind and their eyes.
                        </p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="/eng/rooms" class="history__place">
                        <img srcset="../../img/room1-small.jpg 750w, ../../img/room1.jpg 1200w" alt="Room 1 Image"
